Kubernetes assignment work:
1. creating deployments and services in templates of helm chart
2. testing whether the frontend and backend are running properly in Kubernetes by port forwarding 
3. creating a pv and pvc for the backend data to be persistent even if the pod dies and is recreated
4. creating ingress to route the exeternal traffic into your cluster and accesing it without using ip:port but using a name
5. installing ingress-nginx as the inbuilt ingress-controller traefik doesnt route traffic properly
